{"article_id":"ECopJ1rqMN15l7tS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The impeachment of a president ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"parliamentary esoterica notwithstanding ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"involves three straightforward steps .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"First , the House authorizes the Judiciary Committee to open a formal impeachment inquiry .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Next , that committee conducts an investigation","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"to determine","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"if the president has committed any offense","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"justifying his removal from office .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Finally ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"if such evidence is discovered ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"the full House votes to approve one or more articles of impeachment .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The Democrats ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"despite their accusations of dark doings at the White House ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"can ' t muster enough votes in the House","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to complete the first step","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"toward removing President Trump .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Consequently , Committee Chairman Jerrold Nadler has decided to conduct a fake impeachment inquiry .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Over the weekend , CNN reported","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that the House Judiciary Committee is prepared to vote next week on a resolution","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"laying out the procedures for its investigation :","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" The vote ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"which is expected to occur on Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"will lay out the ground rules","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"for conducting hearings","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"now that the committee has publicly announced","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"it is considering recommending articles of impeachment against Trump. \"","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Nadler has not merely abandoned two centuries of congressional precedent for impeachment ;","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"he is also opposed by nearly half of the Democratic House caucus .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Only 134 of the 235 Democratic representatives favor the maneuver ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"and many adamantly oppose it .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Rep. Tulsi Gabbard","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"( D-Hawaii ) ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"who is running for the Democratic presidential nomination ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"puts it thus :","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"I don ' t support impeachment .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"You know ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"it ' s important for us to think about what is in the best interest of the country and the American people ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and continuing to pursue impeachment is something","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that I think","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"will only further tear our country apart....","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"We need to defeat Donald Trump .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"But I think","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"it ' s important for our country ' s sake and our future that the voters in this country are the ones","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"who do that .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"No wonder","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"the Democratic National Committee arranged the rules","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"so that Rep. Gabbard will be excluded from the next presidential debate .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"She isn ' t in step with the far-left fringe","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that is rapidly taking over her party .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"She does , however , concur with the moderate Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"who are likely to pay the price for Nadler ' s plan","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"to pander to the loony Left .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Virtually none of the 31 Democrats","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"clinging to districts","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"won by Trump in 2016","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"favor impeachment .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"They know","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"the GOP needs to flip only 18 seats in 2020","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"to regain control of the House ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"that the National Republican Congressional Committee","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"( NRCC )","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"has targeted their seats ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"and that Nadler ' s \" inquiry \" may doom their re-election bids .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"As longtime Democratic consultant Douglas Schoen writes :","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"It would be a profound mistake for Democrats to be goaded into pursuing impeachment ... to hold impeachment hearings for President Trump plays right into the president ' s hand ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"by giving credence to his assertion","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"that the Democrats are a party of division , polarization and investigations....","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Getting distracted by impeachment will only impede our chances","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"of developing a narrative","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that can defeat President Trump in 2020 .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Worse , it isn ' t just vulnerable Democrats and cautious consultants","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"who want nothing to do with Nadler ' s irrational push for an expanded impeachment inquiry .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"The voters want these antics to stop .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Since the Russia conspiracy theory imploded ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"the electorate has moved on .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Even dragging poor Robert Mueller before Congress failed to rekindle public interest in that implausible tale .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Every public opinion poll","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"conducted since that embarrassing spectacle","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"has indicated","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that a solid majority of voters are against impeachment .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"More to the point , the electorate isn ' t interested in the \" impeachment inquiry \"","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Nadler is foisting on us .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"The latest Monmouth University Poll , for example , found little support for investigations and less for impeachment :","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Just over a third","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"( 35 % )","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"of Americans feel","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"that Trump should be impeached and compelled to leave the presidency","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"while a clear majority","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"( 59 % )","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"disagree with this course of action....","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"Overall , 41 % of Americans say","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"it is a good idea for the House Judiciary Committee to conduct an inquiry","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"which may or may not lead to impeachment ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"but more","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"( 51 % )","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"say","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"even this initial step is a bad idea .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"So , what precisely is Nadler up to ?","depth":4},{"id":99,"text":"This character has been in Congress since 1992 .","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"Is he so consumed by his antipathy for President Trump","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"that he simply doesn ' t care about two centuries of congressional precedent on impeachment , the risk","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that his party will seem in thrall to a radical Left","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"interested in nothing","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"beyond undoing the 2016 election ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"the perception","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that he and his fellow Democrats couldn ' t care less about the will of the voters ?","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Or is it that his decades-long sojourn in the Swamp has taught him to recognize the need for desperate measures ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that something","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"- anything -must be done","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"to prevent Trump from being reelected","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"while the GOP recaptures the few seats","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"it needs","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"to deprive the Democrats of their House majority ?","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"This latest gambit is so outrageous","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"that Sen. Doug Collins","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"( R-Ga. ) ,","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Ranking Member of the Judiciary Committee ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"told Fox News","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"that he felt sorry for Nadler .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"In a discussion with Maria Bartiromo on Sunday Morning Futures , Collins said ,","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"\" This is really pathetic .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Nothing like this has ever happened in the House before....","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"If they really want to do this ,","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"they have to bring impeachment to the floor .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"This is simply a show. \"","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"Bartiromo suggested","depth":4},{"id":127,"text":"that it was a publicity stunt","depth":5},{"id":128,"text":"driven in part by Nadler ' s desire","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"to avoid a primary challenge next year from the Left .","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"Nadler knows","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"his committee ' s recommendations will never reach the floor of the the House for a vote .","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"Perhaps his fake impeachment inquiry is about nothing more than defending his soft congressional seat .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":265,"left":230,"right":264,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":230,"left":143,"right":229,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":135,"right":142,"rela